Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:44.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}心中却深知再也没有「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:48.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}人生地疏的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:51.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}我们在此相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:58.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}不知何时 微风在身边刮起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}但我并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:07.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(610,180)}我只能尽力去传达
